articles.author: Daniel Arkin
articles.title: The Kessler Twins, German entertainment duo, die together by assisted suicide - NBC News
articles.description: Alice and Ellen Kessler, German twin sisters whose singing and dancing talents made them famous across Europe in the 1950s and '60s, died by joint assisted suicide on Monday, according to the German Society for Humane Dying
